data.description:
Don't miss this beautiful home on a large lot that qualifies for 100% USDA Financing. This home features a open floor plan with an eat-in kitchen, stainless steel appliances, granite counter tops, stunning wood floors, and a large great room with gas fireplace. The owner suite has a separate shower and garden tub with double vanities and TWO large closets.
The home also has a large back yard with a deck facing the woods for extra privacy and endless entertainment possibilities! 
Special features on this home also include a large mud room and butlers pantry.
Seller will include $2500 credit for paint, upgrades, or closing cost! 
Schedule your showing today!
